Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.03,0:00:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气真好  好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭团饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  由乃的包  是不是特别大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:00:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  我想今天应该是正常的上课日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HC080FF&}{\bord0}{\fs27}{\an8}「9月28日  裤裤妖怪」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易到了吃午饭…的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不能和由由一起吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上是运动会执行委员的集会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你  便当
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面的是饭团哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得在工作之余  吃起来也很方便
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:02:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你  茶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过小宫  你为什么成为运动会执行委员了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  问得好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有很深奥的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由你不记得什么时候决定好执行委员的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是解开谜团的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我得了感冒休息了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确答案是那时候由由在睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那么成为执行委员的理由是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后睡迷糊时好像把手举起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是深奥的原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\1c&H0F0F0F&}偷偷×摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒怪兽了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里果然连中午都好昏暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  门开着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FIGHT  FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:12.00,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1}{\shad1}{\fad(200,200)}窓の外にね広がる  青い空を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:12.00,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\bord1}{\shad1}{\fad(200,200)}抬头仰望在窗外开阔的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来听我唱的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦  就给一点点  稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从初中时代开始就很喜欢屋顶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里既是学校的里面  却又是学校的外面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉即使是平凡的我也能稍微展露才华
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空无限高  一望无际
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我们那无限延伸下去的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沙英学姐和弘学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开始上课了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是体育课  快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷电攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手臂痛得发麻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好是第五堂课
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 宫子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.33,0:08:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找弘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近休息时间还有回去时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常不见到她人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为了解弘学姐的一切的话就大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开扣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃的下面…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动衫的上衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我中途脱下来后放在舞台边上就忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先拿好东西回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传球传球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:08:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是可疑人的话怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在的话怎么办  在的话怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐  弘学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 怎么会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O  RU  KO  KI  SO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人留下的犯罪线索？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要坐到正好当中哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一边保持平衡  一边把脚放上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘  再休息一下是不是比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有关系了  在保健室里休息好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  抱歉吓到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬运起来可真是太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐没有什么事的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才真是吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  醒过来时在保健室的床上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在学校里面  宫子来叫我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像只是晕了过去 不用担心没有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑原老师  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:11:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过为什么会晕倒在那种地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是小宫没有来的话  我一个人是搬不动的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很想问问本人  但是现在把她叫起来不太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.43,0:11:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲亲的话会不会醒过来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…吉野  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还发生了那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  大家说一起去体育馆看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了午饭之后就觉得困了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 你在想些什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃  弘倒下的地方是舞台的后面？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是地下室的地下通道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是山吹高中的七大不可思议事件的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说地下通道的正下面有恶灵居住着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:12:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要通过地下通道的戏剧部成员一个接一个倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共计七次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这就是七大不可思议事件的全部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到现场会明白什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师很闲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很闲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顶棚很低呢  好像要敲到头了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想由乃就不需要弯下腰了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿衣镜？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山吹高中里只有在这里和美术准备室才有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的绝对是私人物品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘是怎样倒下来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:12:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里  不知道为什么穿着外裤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉笔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  宫子  不要做些不吉利的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫迪里阿尼式～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}注：阿米地奥·莫迪里阿尼（Amedeo Modigliani , 1884-1920）意大利画家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打从心底里嫉妒你的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门开着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说这里是戏剧部的活动室  不如说是服装室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是能在舞台的后面能换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  由由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  小宫  看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是弗兰肯的头套哦  试试看试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？弗兰肯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}{\bord0}注：玛丽·谢莉（1797-1851 , 英国小说家）所写小说的主人公，\N收集罪犯尸体的部件，把它移植到精神异常者的脑内，\N通入高压电流而苏醒的人造人。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要制造出像我这样的人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了很多事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿衣镜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谜样裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息时间的失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少见地买了一条裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点紧  想努力到可以穿上为止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然每天都去穿衣镜那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为乱减肥而倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我撤回前言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是知道弘学姐一切的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开我玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗是吗  说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得正好  可以帮我一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子穿着那么紧的裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想帮她脱却脱不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  宫子  马上解决吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面的裤裤也一起脱掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐  吃这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起干红薯片  弘学姐更加重要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘  要好好吃饭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦  一定要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛  真让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  晕倒的理由不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是少见地买了条裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点紧  想努力到可以穿上为止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都去穿衣镜那里  到这里还是说中的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有乱减肥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裤子还差一点点就可以穿到屁股了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边拉裤子  一边用力跳了一下后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头就撞到了顶棚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到戏剧部的衣服居然那么充实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜子中到底映出了一个怎样的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运气不好的是  吉野屋老师没有被任何人发现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后防范的安全系统开始运行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上的校舍中响彻无法出来的吉野屋老师的抽噎声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山吹高中诞生了第八个不可思议事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救护车  救护车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是要减肥  晚饭就吃沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要想什么减肥  吃喜欢吃的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐对身体不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…  那就猪肉片沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪肉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次弘学姐为我们做的夹了好几层的炸猪排太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油炸的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生姜烧之类的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}注：生姜烧，烤浸泡过的肉，上面浇上加入生姜汁作料的料理，一般猪肉用得多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的样子  肚子有点饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去做晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐  要是觉得「饭差不多吃到这里吧」的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫子我就在202室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从一开始就打算不要做太多的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为吃太多就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说多咬几下慢慢吃比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.63,0:17:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概一口咬几下？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  由由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有奇怪的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过203没有人住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  一直是空房间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉运动得不少了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放弃再稍微继续下去就好的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  明天开始努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音之前就有了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我住的时候开始  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐  以前住在203室的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘  那个还…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么  有什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么都没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.22,0:18:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  我开门了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.23,0:19:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是过来拿走的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有这么多吗  还是下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  那么就下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房东姐姐  钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁起来比较好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么  什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  有谁来过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.11,0:19:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是房东姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说嘛 弘学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐和小宫怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得没有什么可介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些是减肥用的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,减肥…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.54,0:20:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的 还有这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐以前住在203的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是203的配置？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是弘学姐的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是房东姐姐拿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个一个拿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工的时候说是要不要试用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  打工减肥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有做了  但是房东姐姐都不拿回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那效果怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都做了那么多了 至少有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才不想说的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  这个事情不要说出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:20:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保密吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:20:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.66,0:21:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后会告诉我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两人都不是擅长保密的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是个奇怪的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天举行的全世界雪橇滑降大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主办方顽固地要求中止比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了很多奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪流满面…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的直到早上才能出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫～！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  直到由由睡着为止我都陪着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.59,0:21:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:07.50,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1}{\shad1}{\fad(200,200)}窓の外にね広がる  青い空を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:07.50,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\bord1}{\shad1}{\fad(200,200)}抬头仰望在窗外开阔的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.94,0:22:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HC080FF&}{\bord0}{\fs27}{\an8}9月28日  完  待续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我大家不想回想起来的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来！之前我弄丢了仅剩的500日元
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.20,0:23:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想起来还会哭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.58,0:23:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出荨麻疹的时候  脸肿起来  我大受打击
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.42,0:23:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不想回忆起体重的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.00,0:23:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.47,0:23:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.76,0:24:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃～就你不说太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.57,0:24:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是敏感的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.88,0:24:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集「7月7日  不可以看」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在向阳庄等你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.38,0:24:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必要来看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.03,0:01:06.42,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}嘿哟！嘿哟哟！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:09.22,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}唉呀唉呀唉呀唉呀唉呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:14.46,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}悠闲悠闲悠闲自得地  来做些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.67,0:01:19.71,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}总之  先来下嘿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:22.58,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}嘿哟！嘿哟哟！嘿！哟！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.99,0:01:26.39,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}嘿哟！嘿哟哟！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:34.15,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}不着边际的回答也是木星人的常识
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:39.15,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}起飞了模棱两可的火箭的心正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.28,0:01:44.11,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}幸福地打盹之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:49.50,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}果然果然还是打着哈欠渗出眼泪…早上好
